<sect1 id="ISOIsLongYear">
  <title>ISOIsLongYear</title>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">STD.Date.ISOIsLongYear<indexterm>
      <primary>STD.Date.ISOIsLongYear</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>ISOIsLongYear</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis> <emphasis>year</emphasis> <emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colwidth="80.50pt"/>

      <colspec/>

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry><emphasis>year</emphasis></entry>

          <entry>An INTEGER2 year value.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Return:</entry>

          <entry>ISOIsLongYear returns TRUE if the year has 53 ISO weeks,
          FALSE otherwise.</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

  <para>The <emphasis role="bold">ISOIsLongYear</emphasis> function returns
  TRUE if the specified year is a long year (i.e., has 53 ISO weeks), or FALSE
  if it has 52 weeks.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

  <programlisting format="linespecific" lang="ECL_Runnable">IMPORT STD;
Y := 2020;
IsLong := STD.Date.ISOIsLongYear(Y);
         // IsLong is TRUE for 2020 (it is a long year)
OUTPUT(IsLong);</programlisting>

  <para/>
</sect1>
